des:
Use this skill to get daily theory thrown at you from the CFA Level 1 June 2019 curriculum. This Alexa Skill is NOT affiliated to the CFA Institute and is NOT official CFA Prep material.

The skill will start right away when initiated by "Open CFA Prep" or "Start CFA Prep"
You can then exit the skill by saying "exit" or ask for more by saying phrases like "more" or "another one".

This skill was built with love by VoiceApps.com. Visit us to create your own skill in minutes!
